{"tid":2370834,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"基沙文：我很憤怒 巴塞就沒人站出來喊一喊","createTime":"2021-01-18T10:02:26.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-18T16:57:45.000Z","uid":173952,"like":6,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"ee45c1f8153115568a4aa91f5a5e3fb874fbe506","tid":2370834,"uid":173952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T10:02:26.000Z","msg":"巴塞隆拿2比3輸給畢爾包，無緣西班牙超級盃冠軍。基沙文賽後表示，他非常氣惱。<br />\n<br />\n  「我很憤怒，生氣，煩躁，」基沙文對《Movistar》說，「輸掉一場決賽後，你可能有各種糟糕的感覺。」<br />\n<br />\n  「我們知道對手壓迫的很好，他們表現很好，但我們犯了這麼多戰略上的錯誤。」<br />\n<br />\n  「我們防守很爛，死球時也沒有溝通交流，一些重要的細節，包括何時解圍、何時需要壓出去，需要有人喊一喊。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b139f346b74d4ba9495fb66f7312ea14fba136c","tid":2370834,"uid":3747,"like":2,"dislike":5,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T10:03:55.000Z","msg":"又屌霉西<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47efd37ba1666387cf19d352656656308beb5b4e","tid":2370834,"uid":199804,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T10:08:22.000Z","msg":"有超級盃亞軍算好啦"},{"pid":"a99f8493cd6b0c5797a1f1600159f71b807630cd","tid":2370834,"uid":7917,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T10:20:33.000Z","msg":"樓主你條女知唔知你係雞蟲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e17464515097c75940d3105e608981f6ef8d22c9","tid":2370834,"uid":43785,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"9b139f346b74d4ba9495fb66f7312ea14fba136c","tid":2370834,"uid":3747,"like":2,"dislike":5,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T10:03:55.000Z","msg":"又屌霉西<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T10:20:47.000Z","msg":"又賴隊長問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bac920b68a809e41da353221497e76a6a4320f4c","tid":2370834,"uid":153258,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T10:21:43.000Z","msg":"憤怒 咁佢又